This is an implementation of the Game of Life kata written in python using 
an object oriented + test driven development approach.

See https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conway%27s_Game_of_Life for some interesting patterns.
We use Blinker for most test, and Blinker and Glider for showing off in app.py.

Python: 3.11.4
Packages: pytest, pylint

To run the application:
    python app.py

To run the test:
    pytest

To lint the project:
    find . -type f -name "*.py" | xargs pylint
